        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2165593871" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13263439968213233331">Appanah writes beautifully. Set in Mauritius, this book delves into a little known prison camp for immigrant Jews from Nazi occupied Austria and the Czech Republic whose ship had been turned away from Haifa which was then in Palestine. They were imprisoned for four years. The book, told from the point of few of a young boy is riveting. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


