<div id="review_4342350096" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4342350096" />
    <a title="Julia Nemy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/81622489-julia-nemy"><img alt="Julia Nemy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1525576295p2/81622489.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4342350096?book_show_action=true">Jan 13, 2022</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Julia Nemy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Julia Nemy" href="/user/show/81622489-julia-nemy">Julia Nemy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/81622489-julia-nemy?shelf=translated-literature">translated-literature</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/81622489-julia-nemy?shelf=translated-from-french">translated-from-french</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4342350096" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9947689711421613842">I loved Nathacha Appanah&apos;s book, &quot;Tropic of Violence&quot; and was so excited when she was supposed to visit Aix-Marseille a few months ago (sadly, it was canceled). However, I didn&apos;t connect as much to &quot;The Last Brother&quot;. For me, the story was just okay, but I did find it really interesting/shocking to learn about Jews being sent to concentration camps in Mauritius during World War II. It is definitely a subject I would like to learn more about and I hope to read more of Appanah&apos;s books soon.</span>
  <span id="freeText9947689711421613842" style="display:none">I loved Nathacha Appanah's book, "Tropic of Violence" and was so excited when she was supposed to visit Aix-Marseille a few months ago (sadly, it was canceled). However, I didn't connect as much to "The Last Brother". For me, the story was just okay, but I did find it really interesting/shocking to learn about Jews being sent to concentration camps in Mauritius during World War II. It is definitely a subject I would like to learn more about and I hope to read more of Appanah's books soon.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9947689711421613842" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


