<span id="freeTextContainer15731793262058590379">Heart touching, and narrated in first person from the voice of a 10 year old boy, it presents a story of loss and strength so remarkable in transcending the bonds of blood relationships that the one might get compelled to think of similar relationships in ones life and once finding it, might consume the story as ones own.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


